  "learning_summary": [
    "2026-05-11~12: Strong acceptance for retro cinema posters, friend-to-couple transformations, and emotional/childhood-adult portraits. Static-to-dance/photo-to-video AI tools show high viral potential due to extreme user friction reduction (one-click upload/generate), but UA feedback indicates IP/music dependencies warrant a 'medium/watch' stance. Prioritize low-barrier template generators and emotion/aesthetic hooks. Demote IP-heavy, high-complexity, or saturated duplicate formats.",
