    "2026-05-27 X manual feedback: treat Vogue/fashion-illustration GPT Image prompt posts as duplicate visual material when a recent similar Ciri_ai/Vogue hand-drawn fashion workflow already exists; reject prompt-gallery/resource-aggregation posts such as free prompt galleries or copy-prompt libraries as unrelated even if they mention GPT Image/Seedance.",
    "2026-05-28 feedback tuned scoring and topics.",
