    "2026-06-08 feedback: High acceptance for Hypic template combined with Gemini AI double exposure and light/shadow prompts for artistic portraits. Reject traditional MTB/cycling cinematic edits lacking AI elements (reiterated). Reject multi-panel commercial storyboard prompts (e.g., 9-panel fashion ad on TapNow/Seedance) as they lack broad user-template reuse. Medium acceptance for ChatGPT multi-pose fashion editorial prompt workflows due to strong visual impact and low barrier.",
